metadata.name: The Reunion
metadata.description: Monty is a co-founder of the hip-hop group Remy Boyz, which includes Fetty Wap and P-Dice. Remy Boyz' new song, The Reunion, is one of the first music video NFTs exclusively on HUMBL Gallery. Monty continues to push the envelope on his musical and artistic journey with this exclusive debut NFT collection.
